  },
  {
    eyebrow: "B",
    title: "Content Engine",
    body: "Programmatic content trained on every interview, sales call, and post you've ever written. No generic AI slop.",
  },
  {
    eyebrow: "C",
    title: "RevOps Stack",
    body: "HubSpot wired to your outbound, your enrichment, and your reporting. One source of truth, one weekly review.",
  },
  {
    eyebrow: "D",
